            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Divina singularisque <note>sic</note> clementia <lb n="2"/>dominorum nostrorum <lb n="3"/>Constantini Maximi Victoris <lb n="4"/>semper Augusti <lb n="5"/>et <del rend="erasure">Crispi</del> et Constantini <expan><abbr>nobb</abbr><ex>ilissimorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Caess</abbr><ex>arum</ex></expan> interruptum iter pontis signini <lb n="7"/>operis refectione restitui sua <lb n="8"/>pecunia iusserunt <lb n="9"/>curante pubblice <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Ceionio Caecina <lb n="10"/>Vero <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> curatore <expan><abbr>alv</abbr><ex>ei</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tib</abbr><ex>eris</ex></expan> et cloacarum <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>u</abbr><ex>rbis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>evoto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umini</ex></expan> ma<expan><ex>iestati</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> eorum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: vor dem 8. November 324 n. Chr. (B): Floriani Squarciapino, AE 1975, CIL: keine Angabe der Zeilenfälle; Z. 10: cur(atore), Tiberis.</p>
            </div>
